24namespace rx
25{
26RenderbufferGL::RenderbufferGL(const gl::RenderbufferState &state, GLuint id)
27 : RenderbufferImpl(state), mRenderbufferID(id)
28{}
29
30RenderbufferGL::~RenderbufferGL()
31{
32 ASSERT(mRenderbufferID == 0);
33}
34
35void RenderbufferGL::onDestroy(const gl::Context *context)
36{
37 StateManagerGL *stateManager = GetStateManagerGL(context);
38 stateManager->deleteRenderbuffer(mRenderbufferID);
39 mRenderbufferID = 0;
40}
41
42angle::Result RenderbufferGL::setStorage(const gl::Context *context,
43 GLenum internalformat,
44 GLsizei width,
45 GLsizei height)
46{
47 const FunctionsGL *functions = GetFunctionsGL(context);
48 StateManagerGL *stateManager = GetStateManagerGL(context);
49 const angle::FeaturesGL &features = GetFeaturesGL(context);
50
51 stateManager->bindRenderbuffer(GL_RENDERBUFFER, mRenderbufferID);
52
53 nativegl::RenderbufferFormat renderbufferFormat =
54 nativegl::GetRenderbufferFormat(functions, features, internalformat);
55 ANGLE_GL_TRY_ALWAYS_CHECK(
56 context, functions->renderbufferStorage(GL_RENDERBUFFER, renderbufferFormat.internalFormat,
57 width, height));
58
59 mNativeInternalFormat = renderbufferFormat.internalFormat;
60
61 return angle::Result::Continue;
62}
63
64angle::Result RenderbufferGL::setStorageMultisample(const gl::Context *context,
65 GLsizei samples,
66 GLenum internalformat,
67 GLsizei width,
68 GLsizei height,
69 gl::MultisamplingMode mode)
70{
71 // Note: GL_EXT_multisampled_render_to_texture is not supported in the GL backend.
72 // http://anglebug.com/2894
73 ASSERT(mode == gl::MultisamplingMode::Regular);
74
75 const FunctionsGL *functions = GetFunctionsGL(context);
76 StateManagerGL *stateManager = GetStateManagerGL(context);
77 const angle::FeaturesGL &features = GetFeaturesGL(context);
78
79 stateManager->bindRenderbuffer(GL_RENDERBUFFER, mRenderbufferID);
80
81 nativegl::RenderbufferFormat renderbufferFormat =
82 nativegl::GetRenderbufferFormat(functions, features, internalformat);
83 ANGLE_GL_TRY_ALWAYS_CHECK(
84 context, functions->renderbufferStorageMultisample(
85 GL_RENDERBUFFER, samples, renderbufferFormat.internalFormat, width, height));
86
87 mNativeInternalFormat = renderbufferFormat.internalFormat;
88
89 return angle::Result::Continue;
90}
91
92angle::Result RenderbufferGL::setStorageEGLImageTarget(const gl::Context *context,
93 egl::Image *image)
94{
95 ImageGL *imageGL = GetImplAs<ImageGL>(image);
96 return imageGL->setRenderbufferStorage(context, this, &mNativeInternalFormat);
97}
98
99GLuint RenderbufferGL::getRenderbufferID() const
100{
101 return mRenderbufferID;
102}
103
104angle::Result RenderbufferGL::initializeContents(const gl::Context *context,
105 const gl::ImageIndex &imageIndex)
106{
107 BlitGL *blitter = GetBlitGL(context);
108 return blitter->clearRenderbuffer(context, this, mNativeInternalFormat);
109}
110
111GLenum RenderbufferGL::getNativeInternalFormat() const
112{
113 return mNativeInternalFormat;
114}
